description: Stardew Farmer is a useful helper for players of the game Stardew Valley. It provides seasonal planting and days to harvest information for all crops. For example, you may ask, "When should I plant cauliflower?" and Stardew Farmer will respond with the season in which cauliflower grows as well as how many day until harvest, and any other details about the crop.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask star dew farmer about cauliflower
Alexa, ask star dew farmer when I should plant kale
name: Stardew Farmer
